\c 30
\nb
\v 1 Kwathi uRasheli esebonile ukuthi wayengamzaleli uJakobe\x + 29.31.\x*, uRasheli waba lomona\x + 26.14.\x* ngodadewabo, wathi kuJakobe: Nginika abantwana, kodwa nxa kunge\add njalo\add* ngife.
\v 2 Ngakho lwavutha ulaka lukaJakobe kuRasheli, wathi: Ngisesikhundleni sikaNkulunkulu okwenqabele isithelo sesizalo yini\x + 16.2.\x*?
\v 3 Wasesithi: Khangela, incekukazi yami uBiliha\x + 29.29.\x*, ngena kuye\x + 16.2.\x*, ukuze azalele emadolweni ami\x + 50.23.\x*, ukuze lami ngakhiwe kuye.
\v 4 Wasemnika uBiliha incekukazi yakhe abe ngumka\add khe\add*; uJakobe wasengena kuye\x + 16.3; 35.22.\x*.
\v 5 UBiliha wasethatha isisu, wamzalela uJakobe indodana.
\v 6 URasheli wasesithi: UNkulunkulu ungahlulele, njalo uzwile ilizwi lami, wanginika indodana. Ngakho wayitha ibizo layo uDani\f + \fk uDani: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq ukwehlulela.\f*.
\v 7 UBiliha incekukazi kaRasheli wasebuya ethatha isisu, wamzalela uJakobe indodana yesibili.
\v 8 URasheli wasesithi: Ngibindene lokubindana okulamandla\f + \fk okulamandla: \fl Heb. \fq kukaNkulunkulu.\f* lodadewethu, njalo ngehlula; ngakho wayitha ibizo layo uNafithali\f + \fk uNafithali: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq ukubindana kwami.\f*.
\p
\v 9 Kwathi uLeya esebonile ukuthi usemi ukuzala\x + 29.35.\x*, wathatha uZilipa incekukazi yakhe, wamnika uJakobe abe ngumka\add khe\x + 30.4; 29.24.\x*\add*.
\v 10 UZilipa incekukazi kaLeya wasemzalela uJakobe indodana.
\v 11 ULeya wasesithi: Kuyeza ibutho. Wayitha ibizo layo uGadi\f + \fk uGadi: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq ibutho.\f*.
\v 12 UZilipa incekukazi kaLeya wasemzalela uJakobe indodana yesibili.
\v 13 ULeya wasesithi: Kungokwentokozo yami, ngoba amadodakazi azakuthi ngilentokozo\x + Luka 1.48.\x*. Wayitha ibizo layo uAsheri\f + \fk uAsheri: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq othokozayo.\f*.
\p
\v 14 URubeni wasehamba ngensuku zokuvuna ingqoloyi, wafica amamandrake* ensimini\x + Ngoma 7.13.\x*, wawaletha kuLeya unina. URasheli wasesithi kuLeya: Ake ungiphe emamandrakeni endodana yakho.
\v 15 Wasesithi kuye. Kuyinto encinyane yini\x + Nani 16.13.\x* ukuthi uthethe indoda yami? Usuzathatha lamamandrake endodana yami yini? URasheli wasesithi: Ngakho uzalala lawe ngalobubusuku ngenxa yamamandrake* endodana yakho.
\v 16 Kwathi uJakobe esebuya evela emasimini kusihlwa, uLeya waphuma ukumhlangabeza, wathi: Kimi uzangena, ngoba ukukuqhatsha ngikuqhatshile ngamamandrake* endodana yami. Waselala laye ngalobobusuku.
\v 17 UNkulunkulu wasemuzwa uLeya; wasethatha isisu, wamzalela uJakobe indodana yesihlanu.
\v 18 ULeya wasesithi: UNkulunkulu unginikile umvuzo wami, ngoba ngayinika indoda yami incekukazi yami; waseyitha ibizo layo uIsakari\f + \fk uIsakari: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq umvuzo.\f*.
\v 19 ULeya wasephinda ethatha isisu, wamzalela uJakobe indodana yesithupha.
\v 20 ULeya wasesithi: UNkulunkulu unginikile mina isipho esihle; khathesi indoda yami izahlala lami, ngoba ngiyizalele amadodana ayisithupha, waseyitha ibizo layo uZebuluni\f + \fk uZebuluni: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq ukuhlala.\f*.
\v 21 Emva kwalokhu wasezala indodakazi, wayitha ibizo layo uDina\f + \fk uDina: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq isahlulelo.\f*.
\p
\v 22 UNkulunkulu wasemkhumbula uRasheli\x + 8.1.\x*, uNkulunkulu wasemuzwa, wavula isizalo sakhe\x + 29.31.\x*.
\v 23 Wasethatha isisu, wazala indodana, wathi: UNkulunkulu ususile ihlazo lami\x + Isa. 4.1. 1 Sam. 1.6. Luka 1.25.\x*.
\v 24 Waseyitha ibizo layo uJosefa\f + \fk uJosefa: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq ukwengeza.\f*, esithi: IN\sc KOSI\sc* kayengeze kimi enye indodana\x + 35.17.\x*.
\s Inotho kaJakobe
\p
\v 25 Kwasekusithi uRasheli esemzele uJosefa, uJakobe wathi kuLabani: Ngiyekela ngihambe ukuze ngiye endaweni yakithi, lelizweni lakithi.
\v 26 \add Ngi\add*pha omkami labantwana bami engibasebenzele kuwe\x + 29.20,30.\x* ukuze ngihambe, ngoba wena uyazi umsebenzi wami engikusebenzele wona.
\v 27 ULabani wasesithi kuye: Uba-ke ngithole umusa emehlweni akho\x + Eks. 32.32. 2 Sam. 5.8. Dan. 3.15. Luka 13.9.\x*; sengibonile ngokukhangela ukuthi iN\sc KOSI\sc* ingibusisile ngenxa yakho\x + 39.3,5.\x*.
\v 28 Wathi futhi: Ngimisela iholo lakho, njalo ngizakupha\x + 29.15.\x*.
\v 29 Wasesithi kuye: Wena yazi ukuthi ngikusebenzele njani lokuthi izifuyo zakho bezinjani lami\x + 31.6,38-40.\x*.
\v 30 Ngoba okulutshwana owawulakho mandulo kwami, kwaqhamuka kwaba yinkithinkithi; iN\sc KOSI\sc* ikubusisile ekufikeni kwami\f + \fk ekufikeni kwami: \fl Heb. \fq enyaweni lwami.\f*; pho-ke, ngizayisebenzela nini lami indlu yami\x + 1 Tim. 5.8.\x*?
\v 31 Wasesithi: Ngizakuphani? UJakobe wasesithi: Kawuyikunginika lutho, uba uzangenzela le into; ngizabuya ngeluse izimvu zakho ngi\add zi\add*linde.
\v 32 Ngizadabula phakathi komhlambi wonke wakho lamuhla, ngehlukanise lapho yonke imvu elamabala lelamachatha, layo yonke imvu ensundu phakathi kwezimvu, lezilamabala lezilamachatha ezimbuzini, zibe liholo lami\x + 31.8.\x*.
\v 33 Ukulunga kwami-ke kuzangifakazela ngosuku oluzayo, uba usiza mayelana leholo lami, phambi kwakho; konke okungelamabala lamachatha ezimbuzini, lokunsundu emawundlwini, kuyabe kuntshontshiwe uba kukimi.
\v 34 ULabani wasesithi: Khangela, ye, kakube njengelizwi lakho.
\v 35 Wasezehlukanisa mhlalokho impongo ezingamaqamule lezilamabala lazo zonke izibhuzikazi ezilamabala lezilamachatha, lakho konke okulokumhlophe, lakho konke okunsundu emawundlwini, wakunikela esandleni samadodana akhe.
\v 36 Wabeka umango wensuku ezintathu phakathi kwakhe loJakobe. UJakobe waseselusa imihlambi eseleyo kaLabani.
\p
\v 37 UJakobe wasezithathela ingatsha ezimanzi zephophula\x + ch. 31.8-12. Hez. 31.8.\x** leze-alimondi* lezingelamaxolo, webula kuzo imizila emhlophe, wembula okumhlophe okwakusezingatsheni.
\v 38 Wasefaka ingatsha ayezebulile emigelweni lemikolweni yokunathela yamanzi maqondana lemihlambi, lapho imihlambi efika khona ukunatha; yamitha ekufikeni kwayo ukuzanatha\x + 30.41. Eks. 2.16.\x*.
\v 39 Kwathi imihlambi isimithi ezingatsheni, imihlambi yazala amaqamule, alamabala lalamachatha\x + 30.35.\x*.
\v 40 UJakobe wasesehlukanisa amawundlu; wakhangelisa ubuso bomhlambi kwezingamaqamule lazo zonke ezinsundu zomhlambi kaLabani; wabeka imihlambi yakhe yodwa, engayibeki emhlanjini kaLabani.
\v 41 Kwasekusithi loba nini eziqinileyo zomhlambi sezimitha, uJakobe wafaka izingatsha phambi kwamehlo omhlambi emigelweni, ukuze zidabule phakathi kwezingatsha.
\v 42 Kodwa nxa umhlambi ububuthakathaka ka\add zi\add*fakanga; ngalokhu ebuthakathaka yaba ngekaLabani, leqinileyo ngekaJakobe.
\v 43 Lendoda yaqhamuka yaba nkulu kakhulu\x + 30.30.\x*, yaba lemihlambi eminengi lezincekukazi lezinceku\x + 13.2; 24.35; 26.13,14.\x* lamakamela labobabhemi\x + 12.16; 24.10.\x*.
